---
import image from "../../images/identity_design_image.svg";
import logoIcon from "../../images/logo_icon.svg";
import marketingIcon from "../../images/marketing_icon.svg";
import personalBrandingIcon from "../../images/personal_branding_icon.svg";
import corporateBrandingIcon from "../../images/corporate_branding_icon.svg";
---

<section id="identity" class="identity">
  <div class="container intro_container">
    <div class="icon identity_design_image">
      <img src={image} alt="" />
    </div>

    <h4 class="title identity_design_title">web design</h4>

    <p>
      Our web design services can help rediscover your business’s image in the
      Internet marketplace. Whether it’s to increase profits, provide support,
      sell products or promote your brand, allow our web design services to
      bring your company front and center. Established in 2007 on Long Island
      and with offices in New York City, our web design services have a proven
      track record of what it takes to have a successful website.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container definition_container">
    <div class="title">Discovery</div>
    <div class="text">
      <p>
        We start our projects by understanding the scope and requirements. This
        is accomplished by working closely with you to make sure we are all on
        the same page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container services_container">
    <div class="Card logo_card">
      <div class="Card_heading">
        <div class="Card_icon">
          <img src={logoIcon} alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="Card_title">
          <h4>UI-Design</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Card_text">
        <p>
          The “UI” in UI design stands for “user interface.” The user interface
          is the graphical layout of an application. It consists of the buttons
          users click on, the text they read, the images, sliders, text entry
          fields, and all the rest of the items the user interacts with. This
          includes screen layout, transitions, interface animations and every
          single micro-interaction. Any sort of visual element, interaction, or
          animation must all be designed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="Card marketing_card">
      <div class="Card_heading">
        <div class="Card_icon">
          <img src={marketingIcon} alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="Card_title">
          <h4>digital solutions</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="Card_text">
        <p>
          We create your online identity to perfectly reflect your company and
          the message you want to get through to your visitors. We give you the
          tools to be more effective online.
          <br /><br />
          Your digital identity includes not only your web-app, website, but also
          your social media assets, written content and audio-visual content.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .intro_container {
    > .icon {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      > img {
        width: 320px;
      }
    }
    > h4.title {
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      margin-top: 10rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .definition_container {
    margin-top: 10rem;
    > .title {
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      //   margin-top: 10rem;
      //   margin-bottom: 6rem;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .intro_container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      column-gap: 3rem;
      grid-template-areas:
        "image image image . title title title title title title title title"
        "image image image . paragraph paragraph paragraph paragraph paragraph paragraph paragraph paragraph";
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;

      > .icon {
        grid-area: image;
      }
      > h4.title {
        grid-area: title;
        margin-top: 0px;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
      }
      > p {
        grid-area: paragraph;
        align-self: end;
      }
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .definition_container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 10rem auto;
    }
  }

  .services_container {
    .Card {
      margin-top: 5rem;
      &_heading {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      &_title {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      &_icon {
        margin-right: 1rem;
      }
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 10rem auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      column-gap: 13rem;
      row-gap: 7rem;

      .Card {
        margin-top: 0rem;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
